WEBVTT

00:04.972 --> 00:06.605
The hell is this?

00:06.607 --> 00:09.274
[ Scoffs ] I know.
I got one, too.

00:09.276 --> 00:10.876
I used to work
at little caesars,

00:10.878 --> 00:12.778
and now
they send me coupons!

00:12.780 --> 00:15.114
[ Chuckles ]
They've come a long way.

00:15.116 --> 00:16.782
I sold this house
a month ago.

00:16.784 --> 00:19.051
They just slapped on
a new coat of paint

00:19.053 --> 00:20.953
and re-sold it
for double the price.

00:20.955 --> 00:22.821
Wow.
That color is beautiful.

00:22.823 --> 00:25.190
Tell that to the birds
who cracked their skulls

00:25.192 --> 00:26.959
on this sky-colored
death trap.

00:26.961 --> 00:28.794
[ Sighs ]

00:28.796 --> 00:30.496
Oh, I wish I had
the down payment to buy a house

00:30.498 --> 00:32.297
to fix up and sell.

00:32.299 --> 00:35.501
House flipping --
that's where the real money is.

00:35.503 --> 00:37.136
Well, if you ever need
a contractor,

00:37.138 --> 00:38.804
I just finished renovating
our house.

00:38.806 --> 00:39.872
Oh.

00:39.874 --> 00:41.974
Erased all memories
of Marvin's ex,

00:41.976 --> 00:45.144
minus her wall murals, which are
actually quite beautiful.

00:45.146 --> 00:47.846
"Horses through history".
They're nice.

00:47.848 --> 00:49.515
[ Vehicle door closes ]
Flowers for Mrs. Huang?

00:49.517 --> 00:50.849
What? [ Chuckles ]

00:50.851 --> 00:52.317
Who sent me flowers?

00:52.319 --> 00:54.119
[ Speaking Chinese ]

00:58.426 --> 01:00.492
-- Captions by vitac --

01:00.494 --> 01:01.660
