01:01.662 --> 01:03.595
¶ I'm gettin' mine
everywhere I go ¶

01:03.597 --> 01:05.731
¶ if you don't know, homey,
now you know ¶

01:05.733 --> 01:06.999
¶ fresh off the boat ¶

01:07.001 --> 01:09.668
¶ homey, you don't know
where I come from ¶

01:09.670 --> 01:10.869
¶ but I know where I'm goin' ¶

01:10.871 --> 01:12.671
¶ I'm fresh off the boat ¶

